      • afterLoaded

        protected void afterLoaded()
        Description copied from class: CustomCodeStyleSettings
        Fired when settings just loaded.

        When the common version (the CodeStyleSettings.myVersion is not changed, this method is called just after loading. When the common version is changed, this method called after CustomCodeStyleSettings.importLegacySettings(com.intellij.psi.codeStyle.CodeStyleSettings).

        Overrides:
        afterLoaded in class CustomCodeStyleSettings
